headline: IDEX Corporation to Webcast Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Call
summary: NORTHBROOK, Ill., January 12, 2026--IDEX Corporation (NYSE:IEX) will release its fourth quarter 2026 results February 4, 2026, prior to market open.
